1
00:00:08,666 --> 00:00:10,600
♪

2
00:00:12,633 --> 00:00:15,400
Narrator: IN THE FORESTS
OF THE DENTORA REGION

3
00:00:15,433 --> 00:00:19,166
OF THE REPUBLIC OF PADOKEA
LIES A DORMANT VOLCANO

4
00:00:19,166 --> 00:00:22,500
MEASURING 3,722 METERS HIGH.

5
00:00:22,500 --> 00:00:25,133
IT IS KNOWN AS KUKUROO MOUNTAIN.

6
00:00:25,166 --> 00:00:28,133
IT IS HOME
TO A FAMILY OF FAMOUS ASSASSINS,

7
00:00:28,166 --> 00:00:30,133
THE ZOLDYCK FAMILY.

8
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:33,000
VISITORS ARRIVE EVERY DAY

9
00:00:33,066 --> 00:00:35,666
IN HOPES OF CATCHING
A GLIMPSE OF THE MANSION,

10
00:00:35,666 --> 00:00:37,600
WHICH HAS NEVER BEEN SEEN.

11
00:00:37,633 --> 00:00:42,166
IT'S ONE OF THIS NATION'S MOST
POPULAR TOURIST ATTRACTIONS.

12
00:00:43,833 --> 00:00:45,766
♪

13
00:00:49,333 --> 00:00:51,800
( singing in Japanese )

14
00:02:10,365 --> 00:02:13,065
Mrs. Zoldyck:
I HAVE A MESSAGE FROM KILLUA

15
00:02:13,098 --> 00:02:15,765
THAT HE ASKED ME
TO RELAY TO YOU.

16
00:02:15,798 --> 00:02:17,098
"THANK YOU FOR COMING.

17
00:02:17,131 --> 00:02:20,265
"I'M HAPPY THAT YOU DID,

18
00:02:20,298 --> 00:02:23,765
"BUT I CAN'T SEE YOU RIGHT NOW.

19
00:02:23,765 --> 00:02:25,398
I'M SORRY."

20
00:02:26,265 --> 00:02:28,398
( somber chorus singing )

21
00:02:33,365 --> 00:02:36,198
Narrator: GON,
KURAPIKA, AND LEORIO

22
00:02:36,232 --> 00:02:38,032
HAVE ADVANCED A LITTLE CLOSER

23
00:02:38,065 --> 00:02:41,465
TO THEIR DESTINATION,
THE ZOLDYCK MANSION.

24
00:02:42,632 --> 00:02:43,732
MEANWHILE...

25
00:02:43,765 --> 00:02:45,632
( chorus continues )

26
00:02:51,265 --> 00:02:53,265
Killua: I'M HOME.

27
00:02:54,465 --> 00:02:58,265
HAH. NOT LIKE ANYONE'S AROUND.

28
00:02:59,698 --> 00:03:01,105
Illumi: WELCOME BACK.

29
00:03:01,138 --> 00:03:04,938
SO HOW DID WORK GO TODAY?

30
00:03:04,938 --> 00:03:06,938
Killua: JUST FINE.

31
00:03:06,938 --> 00:03:08,205
Illumi: DOES THAT MEAN

32
00:03:08,238 --> 00:03:10,305
YOU FLAWLESSLY DISPATCHED
YOUR TARGET?

33
00:03:10,372 --> 00:03:14,305
Killua: WHY ASK?
I'M SURE YOU ALREADY KNOW.

34
00:03:14,372 --> 00:03:16,438
‐ YOU WERE SPYING, RIGHT?
‐ ( Illumi chuckles )

35
00:03:16,438 --> 00:03:19,772
MOM IS WAITING
TO TALK TO YOU INSIDE.

36
00:03:19,772 --> 00:03:21,472
Killua: DON'T WANNA SEE HER.

37
00:03:21,538 --> 00:03:23,138
Illumi: I SEE.

38
00:03:28,872 --> 00:03:31,372
( girl chuckles )

39
00:03:34,772 --> 00:03:35,938
UH...

40
00:03:44,472 --> 00:03:46,438
♪

41
00:03:58,605 --> 00:04:00,445
Killua: EH?

42
00:04:04,278 --> 00:04:06,712
DID YOU NEED SOMETHING?

43
00:04:06,745 --> 00:04:09,612
Girl: OH. I WANTED TO SAY HELLO.

44
00:04:09,612 --> 00:04:11,312
Killua: ARE YOU NEW HERE?

45
00:04:11,378 --> 00:04:13,645
Girl: I AM. WHILE YOU WERE AWAY,

46
00:04:13,712 --> 00:04:17,112
I WAS HIRED ON AS AN APPRENTICE
BUTLER, MASTER KILLUA.

47
00:04:17,145 --> 00:04:18,312
MY NAME IS CANARY.

48
00:04:18,378 --> 00:04:20,112
Killua: OH, HEY.
YOU CAN HAVE THIS.

49
00:04:20,112 --> 00:04:21,445
Canary: NO, THANKS,

50
00:04:21,445 --> 00:04:23,412
BUT I DO APPRECIATE
THE GESTURE, MASTER KILLUA.

51
00:04:23,445 --> 00:04:25,712
Killua: YOU DON'T
HAVE TO BE SO FORMAL.

52
00:04:25,745 --> 00:04:26,945
JUST CALL ME KILLUA.

53
00:04:26,945 --> 00:04:29,212
Canary: I'M AFRAID
I CAN'T DO THAT.

54
00:04:29,245 --> 00:04:33,978
YOU ARE MY EMPLOYER,
AND I AM JUST A HUMBLE EMPLOYEE.

55
00:04:34,045 --> 00:04:35,045
Killua: WOW.

56
00:04:35,078 --> 00:04:37,078
THAT'S PRETTY STUPID.

57
00:04:41,612 --> 00:04:42,878
( Canary giggles )

58
00:04:42,912 --> 00:04:45,245
Killua: YOU WERE USING
THE SILENT GAIT, WEREN'T YOU?

59
00:04:45,278 --> 00:04:46,445
Canary: THE SILENT GAIT?

60
00:04:46,445 --> 00:04:49,278
Killua: THE ONE
WHERE YOU MOVE SILENTLY

61
00:04:49,278 --> 00:04:51,612
SO YOU'RE
COMPLETELY UNDETECTABLE.

62
00:04:51,645 --> 00:04:53,112
IN THE ZOLDYCK FAMILY,

63
00:04:53,145 --> 00:04:56,612
IT'S ONE OF THE FIRST TECHNIQUES
THAT WE EVER LEARN,

64
00:04:56,612 --> 00:04:58,112
PERFECT FOR ASSASSINATION.

65
00:04:58,112 --> 00:04:59,578
Canary: I DIDN'T REALIZE.

66
00:04:59,612 --> 00:05:02,952
I SUPPOSE IT'S ONE
OF THE MANY TECHNIQUES I LEARNED

67
00:05:02,985 --> 00:05:05,285
WHILE I WAS GROWING UP
IN METEOR CITY.

68
00:05:06,485 --> 00:05:07,552
Killua: METEOR CITY?

69
00:05:07,585 --> 00:05:11,152
Canary: YES.
THAT'S WHERE I WAS BORN...

70
00:05:12,318 --> 00:05:15,152
A CITY THAT'S BEEN ERASED
FROM THIS WORLD.

71
00:05:15,218 --> 00:05:17,952
Killua: HUH.
WELL, NEVER HEARD OF IT.

72
00:05:17,985 --> 00:05:19,485
Canary: WHERE I COME FROM,

73
00:05:19,552 --> 00:05:21,452
YOU'RE ALLOWED
TO DUMP ANYTHING THERE,

74
00:05:21,485 --> 00:05:24,952
WHICH SORT OF EXPLAINS
WHY SO MANY MEMBERS OF THE MAFIA

75
00:05:24,985 --> 00:05:27,418
AND THE PHANTOM TROUPE
COME FROM THERE.

76
00:05:27,452 --> 00:05:29,952
Killua: I'D LIKE TO SEE IT
ONE OF THESE DAYS.

77
00:05:29,985 --> 00:05:33,318
Canary: WHEN YOU DO, I'D BE
HAPPY TO SERVE AS YOUR GUIDE.

78
00:05:33,385 --> 00:05:34,285
( giggles )

79
00:05:35,718 --> 00:05:37,285
( Killua chuckles )

80
00:05:41,618 --> 00:05:44,085
YOU KNOW THE RHYTHM ECHO?

81
00:05:44,118 --> 00:05:46,952
Canary: THE RHYTHM ECHO?
WHAT IS THAT?

82
00:05:46,985 --> 00:05:49,418
Killua: A TECHNIQUE
USING THE SILENT GAIT.

83
00:05:51,485 --> 00:05:52,618
( Canary gasps )

84
00:05:58,485 --> 00:06:01,658
Killua: IF YOU JUST KEEP MOVING
AT A PARTICULAR RHYTHM,

85
00:06:01,725 --> 00:06:02,658
IT MAKES AFTERIMAGES.

86
00:06:02,725 --> 00:06:04,625
Canary: I SEE WHAT YOU MEAN.

87
00:06:04,658 --> 00:06:05,625
( grunts )

88
00:06:07,058 --> 00:06:08,758
IT SEEMS WE HAVE INTRUDERS,

89
00:06:08,792 --> 00:06:10,992
QUITE A FEW OF THEM, IN FACT.

90
00:06:11,058 --> 00:06:13,092
Killua: DON'T WORRY.
MIKE CAN HANDLE IT.

91
00:06:13,125 --> 00:06:14,725
Canary:
MIKE IS RESTRAINED TODAY.

92
00:06:14,758 --> 00:06:16,658
THOSE ARE THE ORDERS
I WAS GIVEN.

93
00:06:16,725 --> 00:06:20,892
THEY WISH TO TEST MY ABILITIES,
SO I MUST COMPLY.

94
00:06:20,925 --> 00:06:22,725
Killua: HMM.

95
00:06:25,492 --> 00:06:27,292
♪

96
00:06:27,325 --> 00:06:28,925
Leader: WE'LL SPLIT UP HERE

97
00:06:28,958 --> 00:06:32,458
AND KEEP SEARCHING THE MOUNTAIN
UNTIL WE FIND THEIR MANSION. EH?

98
00:06:36,125 --> 00:06:38,292
Canary: PLEASE LEAVE RIGHT NOW.

99
00:06:38,325 --> 00:06:40,925
Leader: AND JUST
WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?

100
00:06:40,958 --> 00:06:43,925
Canary: WHO I AM
IS NONE OF YOUR CONCERN.

101
00:06:43,958 --> 00:06:46,558
YOU'RE TRESPASSING
ON PRIVATE PROPERTY.

102
00:06:46,592 --> 00:06:50,058
I CAN'T ALLOW YOU TO PASS
WITHOUT PERMISSION.

103
00:06:51,292 --> 00:06:53,725
Leader: YOU REALLY THINK
A BRAT LIKE YOU CAN STOP US?

104
00:06:53,758 --> 00:06:57,458
LOOK, YOU OBVIOUSLY
DON'T STAND A CHANCE.

105
00:06:57,492 --> 00:07:00,292
STAND ASIDE,
AND WE'LL SPARE YOUR LIFE.

106
00:07:00,325 --> 00:07:02,132
HOW'S THAT FOR A DEAL?

107
00:07:02,132 --> 00:07:04,898
Canary: TAKE ONE STEP
PAST THIS LINE,

108
00:07:04,932 --> 00:07:07,165
AND I'LL REMOVE YOU BY FORCE.

109
00:07:07,232 --> 00:07:08,732
Seaquant: WHAT WAS THAT?

110
00:07:08,765 --> 00:07:10,965
LEAVE THIS ONE TO US, BOSS.

111
00:07:10,998 --> 00:07:13,398
NO REASON
TO GET YOUR HANDS DIRTY.

112
00:07:13,432 --> 00:07:15,132
‐ LET'S GO!
‐ Intruders: YAH!

113
00:07:15,132 --> 00:07:17,465
Seaquant: YOU MESSED
WITH THE WRONG CREW!

114
00:07:17,498 --> 00:07:19,432
♪

115
00:07:34,832 --> 00:07:36,498
‐ ( Leader gasps )
‐ Intruder: DAMN IT!

116
00:07:36,565 --> 00:07:38,332
‐ Intruder #2: GET HER!
‐ ( all yelling )

117
00:07:41,965 --> 00:07:44,132
( all groaning )

118
00:07:57,798 --> 00:07:59,998
( scattered groaning )

119
00:08:00,065 --> 00:08:01,905
Canary: DO YOU WISH TO CONTINUE?

120
00:08:01,938 --> 00:08:04,638
Leader: SHE TOOK DOWN
ALL THESE GROWN MEN

121
00:08:04,638 --> 00:08:07,272
WITHOUT EVEN BREAKING A SWEAT.

122
00:08:07,305 --> 00:08:10,172
ARE YOU A MEMBER
OF THE ZOLDYCK FAMILY?

123
00:08:10,238 --> 00:08:12,072
Canary: CERTAINLY NOT.

124
00:08:12,105 --> 00:08:14,805
I AM MERELY
AN APPRENTICE BUTLER.

125
00:08:14,838 --> 00:08:16,238
WITH YOUR LIMITED ABILITIES,

126
00:08:16,272 --> 00:08:18,972
YOU'RE NOT EVEN A MATCH
FOR THE BUTLERS,

127
00:08:18,972 --> 00:08:21,838
NOT TO MENTION
THE ZOLDYCK FAMILY.

128
00:08:21,905 --> 00:08:23,338
( leader growls )

129
00:08:24,638 --> 00:08:27,805
( yells )

130
00:08:27,805 --> 00:08:29,472
Canary: HOW UTTERLY MEANINGLESS.

131
00:08:29,505 --> 00:08:31,138
♪

132
00:08:37,305 --> 00:08:40,138
AS I SAID, THIS IS MEANINGLESS.

133
00:09:00,578 --> 00:09:01,645
( Leader chuckles )

134
00:09:01,645 --> 00:09:02,945
I'M A HUNTER, KID,

135
00:09:02,978 --> 00:09:06,912
AND THERE'S NO WAY
I'M GONNA LOSE TO A LITTLE GIRL.

136
00:09:06,945 --> 00:09:08,445
( Canary grunts )

137
00:09:10,078 --> 00:09:12,845
( leader laughs )

138
00:09:12,912 --> 00:09:14,645
PREPARE YOURSELF, KID!

139
00:09:14,645 --> 00:09:16,612
♪

140
00:09:18,845 --> 00:09:20,145
WHAT THE...

141
00:09:23,012 --> 00:09:24,812
( growls )

142
00:09:24,845 --> 00:09:26,978
IT'S TIME TO DIE!

143
00:09:31,412 --> 00:09:32,412
( coughs )

144
00:09:32,445 --> 00:09:34,578
( screams )

145
00:09:41,612 --> 00:09:42,978
( Seaquant whimpers )

146
00:09:43,012 --> 00:09:44,645
( yelps ) I'M SORRY!

147
00:09:44,645 --> 00:09:47,112
PLEASE DON'T KILL ME.
I'M BEGGING YOU!

148
00:09:47,145 --> 00:09:48,345
‐ Canary: ZEBRO.
‐ Seaquant: HUH?

149
00:09:48,412 --> 00:09:51,078
Zebro: SO YOU KNEW I WAS HERE,
DID YOU?

150
00:09:51,112 --> 00:09:53,778
Canary: WOULD YOU MIND
TAKING CARE OF THE REST?

151
00:09:53,812 --> 00:09:54,978
Zebro: AH. OF COURSE.

152
00:09:54,978 --> 00:09:56,778
CLEANUP'S MY JOB, AFTER ALL.

153
00:09:56,812 --> 00:09:59,918
BESIDES, MIKE IS STARVING.

154
00:10:01,752 --> 00:10:02,885
( Seaquant gasps )

155
00:10:02,918 --> 00:10:04,285
HUH?

156
00:10:04,352 --> 00:10:06,085
( screams )

157
00:10:06,118 --> 00:10:08,885
NO! SOMEBODY HELP ME, PLEASE!

158
00:10:08,918 --> 00:10:10,052
( sobs )

159
00:10:12,918 --> 00:10:15,518
( Zebro chuckles )

160
00:10:15,552 --> 00:10:17,452
♪

161
00:10:20,352 --> 00:10:23,418
Killua: SO YOU KNEW
THE RHYTHM ECHO ALREADY.

162
00:10:23,452 --> 00:10:24,718
Canary: YES, I DID.

163
00:10:24,752 --> 00:10:26,518
I HOPE YOU'LL FORGIVE ME.

164
00:10:26,552 --> 00:10:27,918
Killua: HUMPH.

165
00:10:27,918 --> 00:10:30,718
YOU THINK
YOU'RE STRONGER THAN I AM.

166
00:10:30,752 --> 00:10:32,785
Canary: ABSOLUTELY NOT.

167
00:10:32,852 --> 00:10:34,618
Killua: OH, REALLY?

168
00:10:34,685 --> 00:10:36,418
I DON'T...

169
00:10:36,452 --> 00:10:38,252
HAVE ANY FRIENDS.

170
00:10:40,118 --> 00:10:43,252
WILL YOU BE MY FRIEND, CANARY?

171
00:10:46,752 --> 00:10:47,718
( Canary gasps )

172
00:10:47,752 --> 00:10:49,618
♪

173
00:10:52,752 --> 00:10:54,585
( somber chorus singing )

174
00:10:59,018 --> 00:11:01,058
I'M SORRY, MASTER KILLUA.

175
00:11:01,092 --> 00:11:02,725
I HONESTLY AM.

176
00:11:02,758 --> 00:11:03,858
( Killua scoffs )

177
00:11:03,892 --> 00:11:06,092
THAT'S SO STUPID.

178
00:11:06,125 --> 00:11:08,258
( chorus continues )

179
00:11:10,125 --> 00:11:12,125
Gon: LET'S BE FRIENDS!

180
00:11:13,058 --> 00:11:14,192
( chorus ends )

181
00:11:18,758 --> 00:11:20,258
( chains clink )

182
00:11:22,092 --> 00:11:23,692
Killua: GON.

183
00:11:24,925 --> 00:11:27,625
♪

184
00:11:27,692 --> 00:11:28,458
HMM?

185
00:11:31,525 --> 00:11:33,592
♪

186
00:11:33,625 --> 00:11:34,858
HEH.

187
00:11:35,958 --> 00:11:38,092
♪

188
00:11:42,558 --> 00:11:44,792
Gon: IS SHE OKAY?

189
00:11:44,858 --> 00:11:45,925
Leorio: SHE'S FINE.

190
00:11:45,958 --> 00:11:49,058
SHE'S JUST LOST CONSCIOUSNESS.

191
00:11:50,958 --> 00:11:52,758
( Gon gasps )

192
00:11:54,958 --> 00:11:56,792
( Milluki growls )

193
00:11:56,858 --> 00:11:57,758
WAKE UP!

194
00:11:59,958 --> 00:12:01,598
Killua: AH.

195
00:12:01,632 --> 00:12:02,398
OH.

196
00:12:02,432 --> 00:12:04,132
HEY, GOOD MORNING, BIG BRO.

197
00:12:04,198 --> 00:12:06,032
WHAT TIME IS IT?

198
00:12:06,065 --> 00:12:07,298
( Milluki growls )

199
00:12:07,365 --> 00:12:09,365
YOU ARROGANT LITTLE PUNK!

200
00:12:09,365 --> 00:12:11,432
Killua: ARROGANT? COME ON.

201
00:12:11,465 --> 00:12:14,698
LOOK, I FEEL REALLY AWFUL
ABOUT STABBING YOU, BIG BRO.

202
00:12:14,732 --> 00:12:17,932
SORRY. I REALIZE
I SHOULDN'T HAVE DONE THAT.

203
00:12:17,965 --> 00:12:19,398
Milluki: YOU LIAR!

204
00:12:23,032 --> 00:12:25,632
( Killua spits )

205
00:12:25,698 --> 00:12:27,698
CAN'T FOOL YOU, HUH?

206
00:12:27,732 --> 00:12:29,365
( Milluki growls )

207
00:12:29,365 --> 00:12:31,532
( cell phone beeping )

208
00:12:33,065 --> 00:12:34,198
YES?

209
00:12:34,232 --> 00:12:36,532
OH! HI, MAMA!

210
00:12:36,532 --> 00:12:37,532
UH‐HUH.

211
00:12:37,532 --> 00:12:38,298
( gasps )

212
00:12:38,365 --> 00:12:41,365
YEP. I UNDERSTAND.

213
00:12:42,232 --> 00:12:45,432
WELL, KIL, YOU MIGHT WANNA KNOW

214
00:12:45,465 --> 00:12:48,898
THOSE FRIENDS OF YOURS ARE
OVER AT THE BUTLERS' QUARTERS.

215
00:12:48,932 --> 00:12:50,365
( laughs )

216
00:12:50,398 --> 00:12:52,198
HOW 'BOUT IT, KIL?

217
00:12:52,232 --> 00:12:53,898
SHOULD I ASK MAMA

218
00:12:53,932 --> 00:12:55,365
TO HAVE THE THREE OF 'EM‐‐

219
00:12:57,032 --> 00:12:59,765
Killua: MILLUKI...

220
00:12:59,798 --> 00:13:02,472
IF YOU SO MUCH AS TOUCH THEM,

221
00:13:02,538 --> 00:13:04,072
( echoing )
I'LL KILL YOU.

222
00:13:04,105 --> 00:13:05,705
...KILL YOU.

223
00:13:09,605 --> 00:13:12,305
Mrs. Zoldyck: I'M SORRY.
HOW RUDE OF ME.

224
00:13:12,372 --> 00:13:17,138
I AM KILLUA'S MOTHER, YOU SEE,
AND THIS IS KALLUTO.

225
00:13:19,705 --> 00:13:22,605
Gon: WHY CAN'T KILLUA
COME TO SEE US?

226
00:13:22,638 --> 00:13:23,705
WHERE IS HE?

227
00:13:23,705 --> 00:13:26,205
Mrs. Zoldyck:
IN SOLITARY CONFINEMENT.

228
00:13:26,238 --> 00:13:27,572
Leorio: WAIT. WHAT?

229
00:13:27,605 --> 00:13:30,305
Mrs. Zoldyck:
BEFORE HE RAN AWAY FROM HOME,

230
00:13:30,372 --> 00:13:32,472
KILLUA STABBED
HIS BROTHER AND ME.

231
00:13:32,538 --> 00:13:34,605
Kurapika:
YES, THAT'S WHAT HE TOLD US.

232
00:13:34,638 --> 00:13:36,372
‐ ( beep )
‐ Mrs. Zoldyck: AND THEN,

233
00:13:36,372 --> 00:13:39,205
BECAUSE HE REGRETTED
WHAT HE HAD DONE,

234
00:13:39,238 --> 00:13:40,805
OUR KILLUA RETURNED TO US

235
00:13:40,872 --> 00:13:45,038
AND ENTERED SOLITARY
CONFINEMENT VOLUNTARILY.

236
00:13:45,038 --> 00:13:48,905
IN ANY CASE, WE DON'T KNOW
WHEN HE WILL CHOOSE TO LEAVE.

237
00:13:48,938 --> 00:13:50,872
‐ ( beeps )
‐ ( gasps ) WHAT?!

238
00:13:50,872 --> 00:13:53,605
WHAT IS HAPPENING?!
WHAT ARE YOU DOING, FATHER?

239
00:13:53,638 --> 00:13:57,738
PLEASE! DON'T DO ANYTHING HASTY!
HE'S ONLY JUST RETURNED!

240
00:13:58,805 --> 00:14:00,212
( knock on door )

241
00:14:00,245 --> 00:14:01,278
Milluki: HMM?

242
00:14:01,312 --> 00:14:02,745
Man: I'M COMING IN.

243
00:14:02,778 --> 00:14:04,778
( door scraping )

244
00:14:08,145 --> 00:14:11,212
I BELIEVE THAT WILL DO FOR NOW.
THANK YOU.

245
00:14:11,245 --> 00:14:13,212
Milluki: BUT, GRANDPA ZENO,

246
00:14:13,212 --> 00:14:15,545
HE ISN'T EVEN SORRY,
NOT ONE BIT!

247
00:14:15,578 --> 00:14:18,612
Zeno: YES, I'M AWARE OF THAT.

248
00:14:18,645 --> 00:14:21,778
YOU MAY GO NOW, KIL.

249
00:14:21,812 --> 00:14:23,145
Killua: OKAY.

250
00:14:27,978 --> 00:14:30,145
♪

251
00:14:30,212 --> 00:14:33,778
MAN, THAT REALLY HURT.

252
00:14:33,812 --> 00:14:35,978
HEY, MILLUKI, YOU'RE RIGHT.

253
00:14:36,045 --> 00:14:38,378
I'M NOT SORRY,
BUT I DO FEEL BAD.

254
00:14:38,412 --> 00:14:42,112
THAT'S WHY I LET YOU SLAP ME
AROUND FOR A LITTLE WHILE.

255
00:14:42,145 --> 00:14:43,745
Milluki: WHAT WAS THAT?

256
00:14:43,778 --> 00:14:47,378
Zeno: OH, KIL,
SILVA WOULD LIKE TO SEE YOU NOW.

257
00:14:47,378 --> 00:14:50,445
Killua: DAD SAID THAT?

258
00:14:50,478 --> 00:14:52,278
OKAY, THEN.

259
00:14:53,978 --> 00:14:56,745
( Milluki groans )

260
00:14:56,778 --> 00:14:58,245
DAMN IT, GRANDPA!

261
00:14:58,278 --> 00:15:01,385
WHY DO YOU ALWAYS HAVE TO GO
AND SPOIL HIM ALL THE TIME?!

262
00:15:01,385 --> 00:15:04,152
THAT'S WHY HE'S BECOME
SUCH A LITTLE PUNK!

263
00:15:04,218 --> 00:15:05,485
( gasps )

264
00:15:06,652 --> 00:15:10,052
Zeno: BECAUSE KILLUA
IS SPECIAL, MIL.

265
00:15:10,052 --> 00:15:12,552
TELL ME. IN YOUR OPINION,

266
00:15:12,585 --> 00:15:15,118
WHAT DO YOU THINK
OF KIL'S POTENTIAL?

267
00:15:15,152 --> 00:15:17,052
Milluki: IT'S INCREDIBLE, SURE.

268
00:15:17,085 --> 00:15:18,385
Zeno: YES. GO ON.

269
00:15:18,385 --> 00:15:20,385
Milluki: I THINK
IT'S SAFE TO SAY

270
00:15:20,418 --> 00:15:21,985
HE'S THE MOST TALENTED ZOLDYCK

271
00:15:22,052 --> 00:15:24,252
IN THE HISTORY
OF OUR FAMILY, RIGHT?

272
00:15:24,285 --> 00:15:27,785
EVEN MAMA THINKS SO,
AND I HAVE TO AGREE.

273
00:15:27,818 --> 00:15:29,552
Zeno: VERY GOOD ASSESSMENT.

274
00:15:29,585 --> 00:15:33,285
Milluki: BUT THERE'S JUST NO WAY
HE'LL EVER BE A GOOD ASSASSIN.

275
00:15:33,318 --> 00:15:35,218
‐ HE'S WAY TOO ERRATIC.
‐ Zeno: ERRATIC?

276
00:15:35,218 --> 00:15:37,652
Milluki: A KID WHO WANTS TO GO
AND MAKE FRIENDS

277
00:15:37,718 --> 00:15:39,385
COULD NEVER LEAD
THE ZOLDYCK FAMILY.

278
00:15:39,385 --> 00:15:42,252
IN THE END, HE'S TOO WEAK,

279
00:15:42,285 --> 00:15:44,418
WELL, MENTALLY, AT LEAST.

280
00:15:44,452 --> 00:15:46,485
Zeno: HMM.

281
00:15:47,618 --> 00:15:49,452
YES. THAT IS TRUE.

282
00:15:49,485 --> 00:15:51,452
Milluki: RIGHT?
TAKE ME, FOR EXAMPLE.

283
00:15:51,485 --> 00:15:54,918
I'LL KILL ANYONE YOU WANT ME TO,
NO QUESTIONS ASKED.

284
00:15:54,952 --> 00:15:56,752
OH! I ALMOST FORGOT!

285
00:15:56,785 --> 00:15:59,385
MY NEWEST BOMB
IS A REAL WINNER, GRANDPA.

286
00:15:59,418 --> 00:16:03,058
IT'S TINY ENOUGH THAT I CAN
ATTACH IT TO A FEMALE MOSQUITO,

287
00:16:03,092 --> 00:16:04,492
AND I RIGGED IT TO EXPLODE

288
00:16:04,558 --> 00:16:06,392
WHENEVER IT SUCKS
ON THE TARGET'S BLOOD.

289
00:16:06,392 --> 00:16:08,725
THE PROBLEM IS THAT MOSQUITOES

290
00:16:08,725 --> 00:16:11,125
AREN'T GREAT
FOR PRECISION TARGETING.

291
00:16:11,158 --> 00:16:12,258
Zeno: MIL.

292
00:16:12,292 --> 00:16:13,792
Milluki: WHAT?

293
00:16:13,825 --> 00:16:15,558
Zeno: YOU'RE A SHARP BOY,

294
00:16:15,592 --> 00:16:18,425
BUT THAT DOESN'T MEAN
YOU'RE NOT AN IDIOT, TOO.

295
00:16:19,592 --> 00:16:23,125
Mrs. Zoldyck: OH,
WHY MUST FATHER BE THIS WAY?

296
00:16:23,158 --> 00:16:24,392
( sighs )

297
00:16:24,392 --> 00:16:27,458
I'M AFRAID
THAT SOMETHING HAS COME UP.

298
00:16:27,492 --> 00:16:28,758
FAREWELL.

299
00:16:28,792 --> 00:16:30,458
Gon: WAIT! HOLD ON!

300
00:16:32,058 --> 00:16:35,958
IT'S JUST THAT WE'LL BE STAYING
IN TOWN FOR A LITTLE WHILE.

301
00:16:35,992 --> 00:16:38,058
PLEASE LET KILLUA KNOW.

302
00:16:38,092 --> 00:16:39,592
Mrs. Zoldyck: YES, VERY WELL.

303
00:16:39,625 --> 00:16:42,492
I'LL BE SURE TO TELL HIM.
GOOD DAY.

304
00:16:45,992 --> 00:16:49,558
Kalluto: WHO ARE ALL OF YOU?
TELL ME.

305
00:16:49,592 --> 00:16:52,225
Gon: WE'RE ALL
FRIENDS WITH KILLUA.

306
00:16:53,092 --> 00:16:54,758
Kalluto: YOU'RE HIS FRIENDS?

307
00:16:54,792 --> 00:16:57,225
Mrs. Zoldyck: KALLUTO!
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!

308
00:16:57,258 --> 00:16:58,492
COME ALONG THIS INSTANT!

309
00:16:58,558 --> 00:17:00,765
Kalluto: COMING! SORRY, MOTHER.

310
00:17:00,798 --> 00:17:02,732
♪

311
00:17:04,298 --> 00:17:05,965
Leorio: IT GOES WITHOUT SAYING,

312
00:17:05,998 --> 00:17:08,232
BUT THESE PEOPLE
REALLY CREEP ME OUT.

313
00:17:08,232 --> 00:17:09,632
AND I BET THEY WERE LYING

314
00:17:09,665 --> 00:17:12,165
ABOUT KILLUA
NOT WANTING TO SEE US.

315
00:17:12,232 --> 00:17:15,098
GON, WE CAN'T
GO BACK THERE JUST YET.

316
00:17:15,132 --> 00:17:17,098
MAYBE WE SHOULD TAIL THOSE TWO.

317
00:17:17,132 --> 00:17:19,898
Gon: YEAH,
BUT IF WE GO FOLLOW THEM,

318
00:17:19,932 --> 00:17:21,498
I'M WORRIED THAT IT WOULD MEAN

319
00:17:21,565 --> 00:17:24,232
A WHOLE LOT OF TROUBLE
FOR HER LATER ON.

320
00:17:24,232 --> 00:17:26,565
Leorio: YEAH. GOOD POINT.

321
00:17:26,598 --> 00:17:27,565
Canary: I WILL...

322
00:17:27,598 --> 00:17:30,565
TAKE YOU
TO THE BUTLERS' QUARTERS.

323
00:17:30,598 --> 00:17:35,565
THERE'S A PHONE THAT CONNECTS
DIRECTLY TO THE MANSION.

324
00:17:35,598 --> 00:17:38,765
IF MASTER ZENO ANSWERS IT,
YOU MIGHT‐‐

325
00:17:38,798 --> 00:17:40,432
Gon: WHO'S MASTER ZENO?

326
00:17:40,465 --> 00:17:43,765
Canary: HE'S MASTER KILLUA'S
GRANDFATHER.

327
00:17:43,798 --> 00:17:45,732
( animal snoring )

328
00:17:51,565 --> 00:17:53,398
Silva: SO, KIL,

329
00:17:53,398 --> 00:17:56,765
I HEAR YOU'VE MADE SOME FRIENDS.

330
00:17:56,798 --> 00:17:58,298
Killua: YEAH.

331
00:17:59,232 --> 00:18:01,172
Silva: AND WHAT ARE THEY LIKE?

332
00:18:01,238 --> 00:18:03,072
Killua: WHAT ARE THEY LIKE?

333
00:18:03,072 --> 00:18:05,772
THEY'RE A LOT OF FUN TO BE WITH.

334
00:18:05,805 --> 00:18:07,672
Silva: I SEE.

335
00:18:10,005 --> 00:18:11,905
HOW WAS THE HUNTER EXAM?

336
00:18:11,938 --> 00:18:13,072
( Killua gasps )

337
00:18:13,072 --> 00:18:15,605
OH, IT WAS EASY.

338
00:18:18,238 --> 00:18:20,138
Silva: SIT OVER HERE BY ME, KIL.

339
00:18:20,172 --> 00:18:21,305
( Killua gasps )

340
00:18:22,305 --> 00:18:24,905
Silva: I WANT TO HEAR
ALL ABOUT IT.

341
00:18:24,905 --> 00:18:26,105
( Killua gasps )

342
00:18:26,138 --> 00:18:29,005
Silva: YOUR EXAM EXPERIENCES,

343
00:18:29,072 --> 00:18:32,138
WHO YOU MET, HOW YOU FELT...

344
00:18:33,438 --> 00:18:37,605
YOU CAN TELL ME
ANYTHING AND EVERYTHING.

345
00:18:37,638 --> 00:18:38,738
Killua: 'KAY.

346
00:18:38,772 --> 00:18:40,572
( brush rustling )

347
00:18:41,605 --> 00:18:43,772
Mrs. Zoldyck:
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

348
00:18:43,805 --> 00:18:46,172
FATHER DIDN'T EVEN ASK ME,

349
00:18:46,238 --> 00:18:50,738
AND NOW KIL HAS GONE OFF
TO LARK ABOUT WITH PAPA!

350
00:18:52,905 --> 00:18:54,572
UNFORGIVEABLE.

351
00:18:54,605 --> 00:18:59,405
Killua: AND THEN
YOU KNOW WHAT GON SAID TO HIM?

352
00:18:59,405 --> 00:19:01,678
HE DIDN'T WANT HIS LEGS CUT OFF,

353
00:19:01,745 --> 00:19:04,145
BUT HE DIDN'T WANT
TO SURRENDER, EITHER.

354
00:19:04,178 --> 00:19:05,312
( Silva laughs )

355
00:19:05,345 --> 00:19:07,645
Killua: HEH HEH.
HE'S SO SELFISH.

356
00:19:07,678 --> 00:19:09,512
Gon: HE'S INTERESTING,
ALL RIGHT.

357
00:19:09,578 --> 00:19:14,112
Killua: AND THEN GON'S OPPONENT
POINTED A BLADE AT HIS FOREHEAD,

358
00:19:14,145 --> 00:19:15,578
AND THAT'S WHEN GON‐‐

359
00:19:15,612 --> 00:19:16,578
Silva: KIL...

360
00:19:19,012 --> 00:19:21,512
DO YOU WANT TO SEE YOUR FRIENDS?

361
00:19:21,578 --> 00:19:23,245
♪

362
00:19:23,245 --> 00:19:25,445
NO NEED TO HOLD BACK.

363
00:19:25,478 --> 00:19:27,745
BE HONEST.

364
00:19:27,745 --> 00:19:29,512
THINKING BACK,

365
00:19:29,578 --> 00:19:34,312
YOU AND I HAVE NEVER REALLY HAD
A FATHER‐SON CHAT BEFORE.

366
00:19:35,578 --> 00:19:39,812
I WAS RAISED BY MY PARENTS
TO BE AN ASSASSIN,

367
00:19:39,845 --> 00:19:42,812
AND I RAISED YOU THE SAME WAY.

368
00:19:44,845 --> 00:19:47,845
BUT YOU AND I ARE DIFFERENT,

369
00:19:47,912 --> 00:19:52,245
AND IT TOOK YOU LEAVING HOME
FOR ME TO REALIZE THAT.

370
00:19:52,278 --> 00:19:54,245
( Killua gasps )

371
00:19:54,245 --> 00:19:57,145
Silva: YOU ARE INDEED MY SON

372
00:19:57,178 --> 00:19:59,852
AND STILL A PERSON ALL YOUR OWN.

373
00:19:59,885 --> 00:20:03,218
LIVE YOUR LIFE.

374
00:20:03,252 --> 00:20:07,785
REMEMBER, YOU CAN COME HOME
IF YOU GET TIRED, SO...

375
00:20:08,885 --> 00:20:11,052
I'LL ASK YOU AGAIN.

376
00:20:11,085 --> 00:20:14,685
DO YOU WANT TO SEE YOUR FRIENDS?

377
00:20:14,685 --> 00:20:15,685
Killua: MM‐HMM.

378
00:20:15,685 --> 00:20:17,685
Silva: VERY WELL.

379
00:20:19,185 --> 00:20:21,518
YOU'RE FREE TO GO NOW.

380
00:20:21,518 --> 00:20:23,118
BUT, KIL...

381
00:20:25,852 --> 00:20:27,452
PROMISE ME ONE THING,

382
00:20:27,518 --> 00:20:31,585
THAT YOU WILL NEVER BETRAY
YOUR FRIENDS.

383
00:20:31,618 --> 00:20:33,085
GOT THAT?

384
00:20:35,452 --> 00:20:38,052
Killua: I'LL NEVER BETRAY THEM.

385
00:20:38,085 --> 00:20:40,185
I SWEAR.

386
00:20:46,552 --> 00:20:47,852
Mrs. Zoldyck: KIL.

387
00:20:47,885 --> 00:20:49,185
IT'S TOO LATE.

388
00:20:49,218 --> 00:20:51,218
THOSE THREE HAVE ALREADY LEFT.

389
00:20:51,252 --> 00:20:53,518
RETURN TO YOUR CELL.

390
00:20:53,518 --> 00:20:56,252
Killua: NO WAY. I'M LEAVING.

391
00:20:56,285 --> 00:20:58,252
Mrs. Zoldyck: KIL!

392
00:20:58,285 --> 00:21:00,258
‐ ( beeps )
‐ ( gasps )

393
00:21:00,292 --> 00:21:02,058
( somber chorus singing )

394
00:21:02,092 --> 00:21:04,192
Killua: STEP ASIDE.

395
00:21:08,892 --> 00:21:10,558
( Mrs. Zoldyck laughs )

396
00:21:10,592 --> 00:21:16,258
OH, KIL, WHAT A SPLENDID
ICY GLARE YOU HAVE.

397
00:21:16,292 --> 00:21:18,792
( chorus continues )

398
00:21:22,692 --> 00:21:25,258
Mrs. Zoldyck: WHAT IN THE HELL
WERE YOU THINKING?

399
00:21:25,292 --> 00:21:26,525
KIL FINALLY CAME HOME!

400
00:21:26,525 --> 00:21:29,458
Silva: LET THE BOY DO
WHAT HE WANTS FOR NOW.

401
00:21:29,525 --> 00:21:31,625
Mrs. Zoldyck: YOU'RE MAD!
LISTEN TO YOURSELF!

402
00:21:31,692 --> 00:21:34,425
IF KIL IS TO BE
HEAD OF THE FAMILY,

403
00:21:34,458 --> 00:21:36,358
THIS STAGE
IS ABSOLUTELY CRITICAL!

404
00:21:36,392 --> 00:21:39,358
Silva: SO YOU KNOW
WHAT'S AT STAKE. GOOD.

405
00:21:39,392 --> 00:21:42,558
THEN STOP YOUR GRIPING,
AND KEEP YOUR MOUTH SHUT.

406
00:21:42,592 --> 00:21:45,525
( laughs )

407
00:21:45,558 --> 00:21:49,092
DON'T WORRY.
HE'LL COME BACK HOME ONE DAY.

408
00:21:50,025 --> 00:21:53,258
AFTER ALL, HE IS MY SON.

409
00:21:55,192 --> 00:21:57,425
Narrator:
KILLUA HAS BEEN SET FREE,

410
00:21:57,458 --> 00:21:59,625
BUT SILVA CONFIDENTLY DECLARES

411
00:21:59,692 --> 00:22:02,365
THAT HE WILL RETURN
AS AN ASSASSIN.

412
00:22:02,398 --> 00:22:06,798
MEANWHILE, GON AND COMPANY
HEAD TO THE BUTLERS' QUARTERS.

413
00:22:06,865 --> 00:22:11,198
WHETHER THEY WILL MAKE CONTACT
WITH KILLUA REMAINS TO BE SEEN.

414
00:22:17,018 --> 00:22:17,818
♪

415
00:22:17,818 --> 00:22:19,984
( singing in Japanese )

416
00:23:36,991 --> 00:23:38,891
♪

417
00:23:41,891 --> 00:23:44,158
Gon: NEXT TIME,
"CAN'T SEE IF YOU'RE BLIND."

418
00:23:44,158 --> 00:23:46,658
EYE FOR AN EYE?

419
00:23:46,658 --> 00:23:48,024
EYE FOR A TOOTH?

420
00:23:48,058 --> 00:23:49,891
Killua: THAT'S TOOTH
FOR A TOOTH.

